8
00:00:18,960 --> 00:00:21,839
Fancy a game of food connections, Rob.

9
00:00:21,839 --> 00:00:25,920
So I'll name a place and you say the first food that comes to mind.

10
00:00:25,920 --> 00:00:26,560
Ready?

11
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:28,080
Yeah, sure, let's go.

12
